Provides easy to use Python VTK writers and a matplotlib like pcolor()
function.

Homepage
--------

http://certik.github.com/visit_writer/

Installation
------------

python setup.py install --home=~/usr

Usage
-----

This should just work (doesn't require any dependencies):

python demo3.py
paraview --data=vwcurv3d.vtk

This requires matplotlib:

python demo6.py
paraview --data=pcolor.vtk
